{"tid":866881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[照鏡啦] 中國大使刊文批瑞典媒體暴政","createTime":"2018-10-18T08:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T09:37:19.000Z","uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4a12c344dd9726743077e5d044ab41e0d492dd29","tid":866881,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:15:01.000Z","msg":"中國遊客上月被瑞典警察帶離酒店事件，以及後續瑞典電視台發布辱華節目，遭中國外交部和駐瑞典大使館強烈譴責。中國駐瑞典大使桂從友在當地《每日新聞網》撰文，批評瑞典部分媒體和記者對中國抱有偏見和敵意，把中國說的一無是處。<br />\n<br />\n桂從友表示，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有些人只允許他們自己歪曲、抹黑中國，卻不允許客觀介紹中國，是典型的媒體暴政和輿論霸權</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n桂從友又稱，歡迎包括瑞典在內的外國朋友提出建設性的意見，但建議和意見應當建立在客觀事實的基礎上，希望這些傳媒能遵循新聞從業者的職業道德，不要戴着有色眼鏡看中國。"},{"pid":"4b0b0bdce3b8c8b6028c431b86fe0f6eb2cb687c","tid":866881,"uid":470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:16:38.000Z","msg":"駐瑞典大使咁岩又係姓 桂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6864509b59e6ffe3a1bd0bdc02b3566d091ef41d","tid":866881,"uid":35430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:14:18.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣書店件事唔夠客觀？"},{"pid":"26383737afc549f327320789d560ce42aa0de828","tid":866881,"uid":32511,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/172252_1277ea288bbf60cdcfb36436882d32f0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F172252_1277ea288bbf60cdcfb36436882d32f0.png&h=5dbbfec4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3991cd83526f5ead0b97708acd6f863045518610","tid":866881,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:30:12.000Z","msg":"No one give a fuck to savages"},{"pid":"1ec0e56f37f6100b4f094355d075c751d6c41180","tid":866881,"uid":2442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:34:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">中國政府只允許他們自己歪曲、抹黑其他人，卻不允許客觀批評中國，是典型的媒體暴政和輿論霸權。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"92ef354b15519582a8244502128df62607ce6e3d","tid":866881,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:34:56.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"8c95580f1cd71d648e4776c9b8de43a128ff38f5","tid":866881,"uid":14737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:37:19.000Z","msg":"媒體暴政? 笑撚死人咩"}]}